<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 22:06:14 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>Khubeza，加沙巴勒斯坦人在饥饿和战争加剧的情况下寻找的野生植物</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-06/ty-article-magazine/.premium/khubeza-the-wild-plant-palestinians-in-gaza-are-foraging-for-amid-soaring-hunger-and-war/0000018e-13b5-d32b-ab8f-bbfd437f0000</link><description>锦葵在交通岛、路边和田野中自由生长，一直是巴勒斯坦的季节性食物。现在，在饱受战争蹂躏的加沙地带缺乏有组织的援助的情况下，它正在为加沙人提供重要的营养和生计</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 21:34:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-06/ty-article-magazine/.premium/khubeza-the-wild-plant-palestinians-in-gaza-are-foraging-for-amid-soaring-hunger-and-war/0000018e-13b5-d32b-ab8f-bbfd437f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列东耶路撒冷发展管理局所有员工被解雇；实施面临危险</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-06/ty-article/.premium/all-employees-of-east-jerusalem-development-admin-fired-implementation-in-jeopardy/0000018e-1570-d8fb-abff-557a3c9a0000</link><description>东耶路撒冷发展管理局负责制定和管理五年计划，并充当居民和当局之间的中间人。一位消息人士称，七名员工被解雇后，“感觉一切都崩溃了”</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 21:16:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-06/ty-article/.premium/all-employees-of-east-jerusalem-development-admin-fired-implementation-in-jeopardy/0000018e-1570-d8fb-abff-557a3c9a0000</guid></item><item><title>10 月 7 日，哈马斯性暴力事件引发疯狂的否认主义狂潮</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-06/ty-article/.premium/the-unhinged-denialist-frenzy-around-hamas-sexual-violence-on-october-7/0000018e-14d0-d2aa-a1be-1dd5f91a0000</link><description>媒体和专家对 10 月 7 日哈马斯性暴力事件进行阴谋性否认，这让他们自己和美国左派蒙羞。但延长加沙战争的呼吁可能会延续针对人质的恐怖行为</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 21:02:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-06/ty-article/.premium/the-unhinged-denialist-frenzy-around-hamas-sexual-violence-on-october-7/0000018e-14d0-d2aa-a1be-1dd5f91a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列士兵在加沙地带南部战斗中丧生； 13人受伤，其中5人伤势严重</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-06/ty-article/.premium/israeli-soldier-killed-in-south-gaza-strip-fighting-13-wounded-five-seriously/0000018e-157b-d7d3-abce-75fb06720000</link><description>该士兵是参谋军士。 David Sasson，21 岁，来自 Ganot Hadar</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 20:49:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-06/ty-article/.premium/israeli-soldier-killed-in-south-gaza-strip-fighting-13-wounded-five-seriously/0000018e-157b-d7d3-abce-75fb06720000</guid></item><item><title>一场又一场惨败：梅龙灾难调查结果也对内塔尼亚胡定罪 10 月 7 日</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-06/ty-article/.premium/one-big-fiasco-mount-meron-disaster-report-also-convicts-netanyahu-for-october-7/0000018e-1508-d2aa-a1be-1dcd1d410000</link><description>该委员会成员对内塔尼亚胡“你不能对你不知道的事情负责”的论点印象不深。一旦预先警告多年的10月7日大屠杀接受调查，他将无法依靠这个辩护</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 19:08:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-06/ty-article/.premium/one-big-fiasco-mount-meron-disaster-report-also-convicts-netanyahu-for-october-7/0000018e-1508-d2aa-a1be-1dcd1d410000</guid></item><item><title>以色列政府：也为暴力侵害妇女的权利而战</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-03-06/ty-article/.highlight/israels-government-is-fighting-for-the-right-to-be-violent-at-home-too/0000018e-14b0-d8fb-abff-55ba1f630000</link><description>以色列国家安全部长伊塔马尔·本-格维尔（Itamar Ben-Gvir）和他的极右翼政党 Otzma Yehudit 一直在努力剥离女性人口，以减缓进展</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 18:27:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-03-06/ty-article/.highlight/israels-government-is-fighting-for-the-right-to-be-violent-at-home-too/0000018e-14b0-d8fb-abff-55ba1f630000</guid></item><item><title>战争中的以色列：您需要了解的信息 – 第 152 天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-06/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-152/0000018e-14f6-d1cc-abfe-d7ff963c0000</link><description>哈马斯消息人士称，与以色列的谈判正处于崩溃的边缘。 白宫称，如果哈马斯同意释放所有病人、老人和妇女人质，则可能停火六周。 也门胡塞武装疑似袭击了海湾的一艘商船美国官员表示，亚丁风暴造成“人员伤亡” ■ 战争开始 152 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 18:19:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-06/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-152/0000018e-14f6-d1cc-abfe-d7ff963c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列下周允许阿联酋资助的人道主义援助通过海上进入加沙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-06/ty-article/israel-to-allow-entry-via-sea-of-uae-funded-humanitarian-aid-into-gaza-next-week/0000018e-1490-d1cc-abfe-d7bd0ca20000</link><description>当地卫生官员称，海上航线的开通预计将导致国际社会对以色列在加沙的人道主义危机提出更多批评，由于以色列在援助物资转移方面设置困难，迄今为止已有 18 人死亡。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 16:56:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-06/ty-article/israel-to-allow-entry-via-sea-of-uae-funded-humanitarian-aid-into-gaza-next-week/0000018e-1490-d1cc-abfe-d7bd0ca20000</guid></item><item><title>尤瓦尔·亚伯拉罕是一位真正的英雄，因为他没有在种族隔离的重压下呻吟</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-03-06/ty-article-opinion/.premium/yuval-abraham-is-actually-a-true-hero-for-not-groaning-under-the-weight-of-apartheid/0000018e-1433-d73e-af9f-7fb7d85a0000</link><description>以色列电影制片人在柏林电影节上的获奖感言似乎冒犯了《国土报》记者的敏感耳朵</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 16:34:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-03-06/ty-article-opinion/.premium/yuval-abraham-is-actually-a-true-hero-for-not-groaning-under-the-weight-of-apartheid/0000018e-1433-d73e-af9f-7fb7d85a0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡和甘茨勉强的政治婚姻显示出稳定的曙光</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-06/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-and-gantzs-reluctant-political-marriage-shows-glimpses-of-stability/0000018e-1283-d547-a19e-92935e450000</link><description>本尼·甘茨的美国之行可能羞辱了内塔尼亚胡，但并没有真正威胁到以色列的战时政府 ■ 总理决定允许斋月期间在阿克萨清真寺进行礼拜自由，这表明了政府极右翼势力的局限性</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 16:27:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-06/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-and-gantzs-reluctant-political-marriage-shows-glimpses-of-stability/0000018e-1283-d547-a19e-92935e450000</guid></item><item><title>以色列批准在约旦河西岸定居点建造3,476套住房</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-06/ty-article/.premium/israels-approves-construction-of-3-476-housing-units-in-west-bank-settlements/0000018e-144f-d792-a7be-3cffd18d0000</link><description>一些单位得到了政府的批准，他们称之为对两周前发生的袭击事件的回应，那次袭击造成一名以色列人死亡、11 人受伤。估计显示，今年批准的约旦河西岸住房数量创上世纪九十年代《奥斯陆协议》以来的最高水平</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 16:20:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-06/ty-article/.premium/israels-approves-construction-of-3-476-housing-units-in-west-bank-settlements/0000018e-144f-d792-a7be-3cffd18d0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡的政党驳回了对梅龙灾难的调查结果，称其为“政治挑衅”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-06/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-dismisses-probe-findings-into-meron-disaster-labels-it-political-provocation/0000018e-13f7-d7d3-abce-73ffca6d0000</link><description>反对党领袖拉皮德在对 2021 年梅龙灾难（造成 45 名极端正统信徒死亡）的调查结果后猛烈抨击内塔尼亚胡，称如果他是一名普通公民，“他今天就会因过失杀人罪被起诉，并去监狱&amp;#39;</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 15:38:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-06/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-dismisses-probe-findings-into-meron-disaster-labels-it-political-provocation/0000018e-13f7-d7d3-abce-73ffca6d0000</guid></item><item><title>复仇、无知和无能：以色列对加沙灾难性的人道主义援助政策</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-06/ty-article/.premium/vengeance-ignorance-and-incompetence-israels-disastrous-aid-policy-for-gaza/0000018e-13f5-d8fb-abff-57ff1e2d0000</link><description>在战争期间的不同时期，当非以色列媒体已经报道加沙的“饥荒”时，以色列官员仍然将对加沙人的人道主义援助视为“哈马斯的生命线”。在过去的五个月里，以色列从未制定过明确的政策允许物资进入加沙地带</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 14:51:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-06/ty-article/.premium/vengeance-ignorance-and-incompetence-israels-disastrous-aid-policy-for-gaza/0000018e-13f5-d8fb-abff-57ff1e2d0000</guid></item><item><title>他的书几乎在以色列被禁。但科勒姆·麦肯对巴以冲突仍抱有希望</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-03-06/ty-article-magazine/.premium/author-colum-mccann-wants-to-humanize-the-israeli-palestinian-conflict/0000018e-1322-d950-a18e-f3bb173f0000</link><description>科勒姆·麦肯的小说《Apeirogon》讲述了失去亲人的以色列和巴勒斯坦父亲之间非凡的友谊，现已出版希伯来语版本。作者不确定这是否是一个时机不佳的情况，或者是以色列人阅读他的书的正确时机</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 12:17:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-03-06/ty-article-magazine/.premium/author-colum-mccann-wants-to-humanize-the-israeli-palestinian-conflict/0000018e-1322-d950-a18e-f3bb173f0000</guid></item><item><title>梅龙灾难：内塔尼亚胡“个人负责”，但不应被免职</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-06/ty-article/.premium/israeli-state-commission-releases-final-report-on-meron-disaster/0000018e-12cd-df16-a58e-1fffe7ad0000</link><description>该国家委员会发现，以色列总理内塔尼亚胡知道或应该知道近三年前在以色列北部梅龙山举行的 Lag B&amp;#39;Omer 庆祝活动期间导致 45 人死亡的危险和风险</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 10:11:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-06/ty-article/.premium/israeli-state-commission-releases-final-report-on-meron-disaster/0000018e-12cd-df16-a58e-1fffe7ad0000</guid></item><item><title>美国在斋月前推动加沙停火，但辛瓦尔似乎支持升级</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-06/ty-article/.premium/u-s-in-final-push-for-gaza-truce-before-ramadan-but-sinwar-seems-to-favor-escalation/0000018e-1073-d343-a9de-397733dd0000</link><description>以色列国防官员怀疑哈马斯领导人希望暴力蔓延到耶路撒冷和约旦河西岸，并顽固地阻挠停火</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 04:01:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-06/ty-article/.premium/u-s-in-final-push-for-gaza-truce-before-ramadan-but-sinwar-seems-to-favor-escalation/0000018e-1073-d343-a9de-397733dd0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列士兵在加沙战斗中丧生、13人受伤；哈马斯称谈判“濒临崩溃”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-06/ty-article-live/idf-hits-hezbollah-launch-sites-used-to-fire-rockets-anti-tank-missiles-at-kiryat-shmona/0000018e-1170-db19-abae-7dfa03270000</link><description>五名以色列国防军士兵在加沙战斗中受重伤 ■ 以色列在耶路撒冷持刀袭击中中度受伤 ■ 哈马斯：谈判濒临崩溃，以色列没有满足我们的主要要求 ■ 胡塞武装称，在胡塞武装袭击造成至少两人死亡后，美国和英国针对也门荷台达机场商业货运的船员 ■ 以色列批准在约旦河西岸定居点建造 3,476 套住房；德国、沙特阿拉伯“强烈谴责”</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 01:56:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-06/ty-article-live/idf-hits-hezbollah-launch-sites-used-to-fire-rockets-anti-tank-missiles-at-kiryat-shmona/0000018e-1170-db19-abae-7dfa03270000</guid></item><item><title>脾气暴躁的以色列高级外交官罕见地赢得了公关胜利</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-06/ty-article/.premium/israels-tramtrum-throwing-top-diplomat-snatched-defeat-from-the-jaws-of-a-rare-pr-victory/0000018e-1073-d343-a9de-39774bd10000</link><description>外交部长卡茨决定召回以色列驻联合国特使——表面上是为了抗议安理会未能就 10 月 7 日的暴行举行讨论——这进一步证明他将政党政治置于任何其他考虑之上</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 23:08:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-06/ty-article/.premium/israels-tramtrum-throwing-top-diplomat-snatched-defeat-from-the-jaws-of-a-rare-pr-victory/0000018e-1073-d343-a9de-39774bd10000</guid></item><item><title>尽管本格维尔提出要求，以色列不会在斋月期间对阿克萨清真寺的礼拜者施加新的限制</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-05/ty-article/.premium/israel-will-not-impose-new-limits-on-worshippers-at-al-aqsa-during-ramadan/0000018e-1006-d917-adce-fd0e271f0000</link><description>针对内塔尼亚胡的决定，国家安全部长本-格维尔指责称，“内塔尼亚胡和战时内阁认为10月7日没有发生任何事情。这一决定将以色列公民置于危险之中，并可能给哈马斯带来胜利的形象”</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 19:22:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-05/ty-article/.premium/israel-will-not-impose-new-limits-on-worshippers-at-al-aqsa-during-ramadan/0000018e-1006-d917-adce-fd0e271f0000</guid></item><item><title>战争中的以色列：您需要了解的信息 – 第 151 天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-05/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-151/0000018e-0fa4-db19-abae-7fae6d6c0000</link><description>布林肯：有机会立即停火，由哈马斯决定是否准备好参与停火 ■ 美国、约旦向加沙北部空投援助物资 ■ 世界卫生组织：加沙北部营养不良“特别严重” ■ 两枚火箭弹黎巴嫩袭击了以色列北部的建筑物 ■ 内塔尼亚胡：以色列将在斋月期间“尽一切努力维护阿克萨清真寺的礼拜自由” ■ 战争结束 151 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 17:46:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-05/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-151/0000018e-0fa4-db19-abae-7fae6d6c0000</guid></item></channel></rss>